==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Protagon
<hw>Pro"ta*gon</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Proto-</ets>
+ Gr. <grk>'agw`n</grk> a contest. See. <er>Protagonist</er>. So called
because it was the first definitely ascertained principle of the
brain.]</ety> <fld>(Physiol. Chem.)</fld> <def>A nitrogenous
phosphorized principle found in brain tissue. By decomposition it yields
neurine, fatty acids, and other bodies.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Protagonist</ent>⟦br⟧
